The background of the portrait is a neutral color, which serves to highlight Socrates and his students and give the portrait a timeless quality. The texture of Socrates' hair and beard has been carefully rendered with small, precise brushstrokes, while the students' clothing and facial features are rendered in a softer, more painterly style.
